$PAR
$PAR

a) Calculate the binding energy per nucleon for \(\,^{12}\textrm{C}\). Stable and relatively tightly bound, this nuclide is most of natural carbon.

$PAR
$PAR

\{ans_rule(40)\} \(\textrm{MeV}\)

$PAR
$PAR

END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp("$binding_energy_per_A_12"));

BEGIN_TEXT
